13. The convection oven of claim 9 further comprising: 
a gas combustion system mounted with respect to the blower plenum, the gas combustion system generating combustion products; 
a heat exchange element mounted within the blower plenum and connected to the gas combustion system; 
a header connected to the heat exchange element, the header in communication with the gas combustion system; and 
an inducer connected to the header, the inducer having a valve moveable between an open position and a closed position.
